      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, a definitive example of Bavarian engineering. This vehicle is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that provides a razor-sharp throttle response up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is in exemplary state, with a verified-intact subframe and original suspension kinematics. Meticulously maintained with a full service history, this M3 retains its factory-applied finish and pristine Nappa leather interior, representing a rare opportunity for the purist seeking a mechanically flawless, unmolested icon.",
